{"tid":1352583,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"呢場反送中到依家有d古怪","createTime":"2019-07-22T20:41:32.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-22T21:14:30.000Z","uid":75542,"like":5,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"dfe4fc37e9c8cac5a7b26626da5f75f66a6026ca","tid":1352583,"uid":75542,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T20:41:32.000Z","msg":"由清析嘅五大訴求<br />\n到尋日黑警突然開曬成個港島任你行任你玩<br />\n之後就中聯辦<br />\n到宣言<br />\n到臨時立法會<br />\n到元朗事件<br />\n依家就爭這光復元朗定主線<br />\n<br />\n感覺到成件事已經唔係五大訴求<br />\n我清楚知道勇武係呢場運動功不可沒<br />\n但係有幾多人接受到呢種轉風向？<br />\n<br />\n你可能覺得唔需要理會<br />\n真係唔需要理會？<br />\n<br />\n兄弟爬山，各自揾食<br />\n係講緊大家用自己方法<br />\n達到五大訴求嘅目的<br />\n<br />\n如果連五大訴求都改<br />\n有幾多人跟得上<br />\n又或者有幾多人跟？<br />\n<br />\n預左俾人鬧一毛<br />\n點都好，我都會跟大家一齊行<br />\n我要代死去嘅義士行落去"},{"pid":"4a809510b47c07301d5b3290ee316ac119fdfa16","tid":1352583,"uid":159089,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T20:43:31.000Z","msg":"五大訴求唔撚改啦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dac494a39a0086ebae9d81e269f202644dbce0fb","tid":1352583,"uid":104767,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T20:44:00.000Z","msg":"鄉黑係政府最後一張牌,絕對係主線,絕對係對準政權<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4bdc84fc16ae41e9927d2fbb60811176a8dad0a1","tid":1352583,"uid":273319,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T20:45:36.000Z","msg":"五大訴求冇變過<br />\n係呢家個政府冇可能滿足<br />\n所以要自己做<br />\n光復香港 時代革命<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0bfd514ca6716f731a6c49221dfd48ddf8fb49d8","tid":1352583,"uid":75542,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"dac494a39a0086ebae9d81e269f202644dbce0fb","tid":1352583,"uid":104767,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T20:44:00.000Z","msg":"鄉黑係政府最後一張牌,絕對係主線,絕對係對準政權<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T20:54:20.000Z"